. Simple I/O example
IOPROG   START   0
         LDX     #0
         LDA     #0
LOOP     TD      INPUT
         JEQ     LOOP
         RD      INPUT
         WD      OUTPUT
         TIX     COUNT
         JLT     LOOP
         RSUB

COUNT    RESW    1
INPUT    BYTE    X'F1'
OUTPUT   BYTE    X'05'
         END     IOPROG